{
  "texts": [
    "To circumvent the internal limit on the size of the product graph, the option \"maxBondMatchPairs\" in the C++ base of RDKit was exposed to Python interface, necessitating recompilation.",
    "Otherwise, all settings were left at their default values.",
    "We now prove that the myopic MCES distance is a metric.",
    "The proof proceeds in four steps: For completeness, we show that the first bound gives rise to a pseudometric.",
    "Next, we show that the second bound is a pseudometric, too."
  ]
}